v1.6.x EXPERIMENTAL ML DEPICT MODULE
====================================
The optional ML 2D-coordinate residual refiner
(editor/MLDepict.js + editor/ml-depict-weights.{json,js}) is a small
neural network bundled inside this distribution under the Apache
License, Version 2.0, together with the rest of BIME.

The weights are BioInception PVT LTD proprietary IP. They run fully
offline as part of the standard BIME bundle. The architecture is too
small to memorise or reconstruct any specific molecule; the model
learns generic 2D-coord refinement statistics, not lookup tables.

Use of the ML refiner is opt-in (Layout.options.useMLDepict = true);
it is off by default and BIME runs identically to v1.5.2 when the
flag is left at its default false.
